uld have commanded them to use the toothstick with every ablution.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 1260 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/prophet-siwak-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":33104,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: The Prophet uses the toothstick often","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI was ordered to use the toothstick so often that I thought something of it would be sent down to me in the Quran or revealed to me.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2998 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/visit-prophet-bad-oral-hygiene\/","url_meta":{"origin":33104,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: You visit the Prophet with bad oral hygiene?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Abbas re